Haven't made this yet, but I intend to make it for a Christmas party this year. To a previous reviewer: Sogginess can prevented by placing the sprinform pan on a large square of heavy duty foil before baking. Fold the foil up around the outside of the pan, making sure that it is completely covered. This will prevent water from seeping in and ruining your crust.

